ad.title: I am a diligent and reliable housekeeper in Paris.
ad.content:
My name is Christian, and I am 32 years old.

I have been working as a professional housekeeper for the past two years, gaining extensive experience in maintaining clean, organized, and comfortable living spaces. I am highly reliable, detail-oriented, and skilled in time management, ensuring that all tasks are completed efficiently and to the highest standards.

I am available on Mondays from 8:00 AM to 12:00 PM and Tuesday to Friday from 8:00 AM to 7:00 PM. I am flexible and willing to accommodate schedules as needed to provide the best service to my clients.

My expertise includes deep cleaning sinks, lavatories, and windows, ensuring they are spotless and sanitized. I am also proficient in ironing clothes to perfection, vacuuming carpets and rugs to remove dust and debris, and mopping floors to maintain a fresh and hygienic environment. Whether it's a routine cleaning or a more detailed task, I always strive to provide excellent service.

Beyond my skills, I take pride in being a hardworking, patient, kind, and trustworthy housekeeper. I treat every home with respect and care, ensuring a comfortable and welcoming space for those I serve. My goal is to make every home I clean a clean, organized, and stress-free environment.

Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to the opportunity to assist you with your housekeeping needs!
